---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { LAST_VERIFIED } from "@/data/tax-constants";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Freelancer Tax Estimator"
  description="Privacy policy for FreelancerTaxEstimator: what we collect, how Google AdSense uses cookies on this site, and your data choices."
>
  <article class="prose-content px-4 py-10">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
      Last updated {LAST_VERIFIED}.
    </p>

    <p>
      FreelancerTaxEstimator.com ("the site") is operated as a free, ad-supported
      educational tool. This page describes what data the site processes, what
      our advertising partners do, and the choices available to you.
    </p>

    <h2>Information you enter into the calculator</h2>
    <p>
      The tax calculator runs entirely in your browser. Income, expense, filing
      status, and other figures you type into the calculator are{" "}
      <strong>not transmitted to any server</strong> and are not stored beyond
      your current browser session.
    </p>

    <h2>Information collected automatically</h2>
    <p>
      Like most websites, our hosting provider may collect standard server logs
      (IP address, user-agent, requested URL, timestamp) for security and
      operational purposes. These logs are not used to build advertising
      profiles by us.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and advertising — Google AdSense</h2>
    <p>
      This site displays advertisements served by{" "}
      <strong>Google AdSense</strong>. Google and its partners use cookies and
      similar identifiers to serve ads based on your prior visits to this site
      and other sites, and to measure ad performance. Specifically:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on this
        site.
      </li>
      <li>
        Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to
        serve ads to you based on your visit to this site and/or other sites on
        the Internet.
      </li>
      <li>
        You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting{" "}
        <a
          href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads"
          rel="noopener nofollow"
          target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a
        >.
      </li>
      <li>
        You may also opt out of some third-party vendors' use of cookies for
        personalized advertising by visiting{" "}
        <a
          href="https://optout.aboutads.info/"
          rel="noopener nofollow"
          target="_blank">aboutads.info</a
        >.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      For more information on how Google uses data when you use our site or
      app, see{" "}
      <a
        href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites"
        rel="noopener nofollow"
        target="_blank"
        >How Google uses information from sites or apps that use our
        services</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand which pages are
      visited and how the site performs. If we add a third-party analytics
      provider that uses cookies, we will list it here.
    </p>

    <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
    <p>
      This site is not directed to children under 13 and does not knowingly
      collect personal information from children.
    </p>

    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Block third-party cookies in your browser settings to prevent ad
        personalization.
      </li>
      <li>
        Use a browser extension or content blocker if you prefer not to see ads
        at all.
      </li>
      <li>Use the calculator without entering any personally identifying information — none is required.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy as the site evolves. Material changes will be
      reflected in the "last updated" date at the top.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy:{" "}
      <a href="mailto:hello@freelancertaxestimator.com"
        >hello@freelancertaxestimator.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
